Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I've been a physician for 35 years and specialized in the field of psychiatry.\NFor years I worked in the field of psychoanalysis and psychotherapy, various forms of psychotherapy and group therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a lot of work on nutrition and its relationship to various bodily diseases, also emotional and mental disorders.\NAnd for the last eight years I've been doing research into the nature of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,exploring that domain which the world calls spiritual, elucidating the basic laws of self-healing,\Ndiscovering what is common amongst all the people I know who have recovered from progressive, serious, fatal, even terminal illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And so in this series, the Sedona series, we're talking about,\Nthe utilization of the basic laws of mind and consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in approaching such serious illnesses as AIDS, cancer, heart disease, hypertension, alcoholism, drug addiction.\NAll of them serious confronts, all of them things that require us to change our view of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is reality?\NAnd so we'll be talking about body, mind, and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about...\NWe'll be talking about the nature of consciousness in today's talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,which is addressed to patients with cancer, to families of people with cancer,\Nto people who fear they might have cancer, to people who are in treatment with cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about a holistic approach.\NSo we're not talking either-or.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:02:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not saying, well, you know, the treatment has to be traditional or an alternate treatment.\NWhat we're saying is and, to include in that larger dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because true healing...\NTrue healing requires the larger dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the people I know who've recovered from these chronic and very severe diseases,\Nmany of them who were given up as hopeless by their physicians in the medical community,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,have recovered and, without exception, they've all done so by exploring a greater definition of the truth of reality,\Nthat which they are, exploring that realm of human knowledge called spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that relationship between body, mind, and spirit?\NYou know, other than a catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something real that you can work with in everyday life and see actual results?\NWell, the friends that walk around who have recovered from all these fatal illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,are the walking evidence that we can all recover from any disease known to mankind.\NI, myself, as I have shared in other series and other talks in this series,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,had 15 or 20 aggressive illnesses, chronic, intractable.\NAlthough they were treatable, some of the symptoms were handled, the diseases did not get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, they were getting progressively worse.\NSo despite traditional medical treatment, I was merely holding the line on a few and losing the line on several.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it was exploring the greater dimension then, exploring those fields called consciousness\Nand how they relate to self-healing, that a recovery from all of these illnesses, without exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,came about.\NThe alteration in the blood chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I once had gout in the high elevated uric acid level.\NAfter I learned that the body only does what is held in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I began to change what I was holding in mind,\Nthen the body's chemistry literally began to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that all the atoms and cells and elements, electrons,\Nall of that which the body has made is conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But the cells of the body are conscious.\NAnd this is very important in the approaches that we'll be utilizing in the treatment of cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the relationship between body, mind, and spirit?\NHe said the principle is that the body reflects that which is held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which is held in mind reflects one's spiritual position.\NAnd so it's necessary to know where all human experience takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if we address that level, we will be addressing the most powerful level.\NIf the physical is the consequence of the mental,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mental is the consequence of the spiritual,\Nthen it is in the area called consciousness itself that we should address ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And clinically this is so.\NPeople who address that level, address the level of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,watch transformations come about in their body\Nwithout even having addressed the body directly in any kind of a medical approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to know where experience is experience.\NAnd let go some of the common illusions which people hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,just because they haven't looked into the matter.\NThe body itself is incapable of experiencing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, my hands as they are crossed here cannot experience themselves.\NThey cannot experience their existence, their position in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the sensations have no capacity to experience themselves.\NIt's because of something greater than the physical body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is what we call mind.\NSo that all the physical, and all that goes on with the physical body, sensations,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is experienced in the greater dimension called mind.\NIt is in mind that the experience of body takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind itself, curiously enough, has no capacity to experience itself.\NA thought, for instance, a thought is just an energy form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A thought has no capacity to experience its own thoughtness.\NA feeling has no capacity to experience its own feelingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,An emotion cannot be experienced,\Nother than the fact that mind itself is held within an energy field that is greater than mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the energy field of consciousness itself,\Nwhich has no dimensions, which has no limitations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and which has no form.\NIt's because of consciousness that we are aware of what goes on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know what's being registered in mind\Nis because of that energy field called consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even consciousness itself is not sufficient.\NThere is an energy field of a very high frequency in vibration,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the same as that of life itself, called awareness.\NIt is out of awareness that there is the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is going on within consciousness,\Nwhich is reporting what is going on within mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which in turn is reporting what is going on with the physical body.\NAnd so you can see the physical body itself is several levels removed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,from that which is the most real,\Nand therefore the most powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We find that the energy of thought is far more powerful\Nthan the energy levels of the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so to understand some of this,\Nwe'll need a context in which to understand the whole field of self-healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In a one hour talk today,\Nwe won't have time to cover the entire field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have covered a number of things that have to be said\Nin other tapes in the consciousness series,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,where we did a tape, a talk on illness,\Nwe did another talk on health,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we did another one on pain and suffering,\Nand there we pointed out that the two are not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:08:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffering is one thing and pain is another,\Nas I know because I just went to the dentist's last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we did another one on stress.\NIt would be good to look at these if you can borrow them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,or get them from somewhere,\Nsee where you can sort of expand your awareness of this whole field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we're talking about, then,\Nthe nature of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we create a context for ourselves,\Nso that the self-healing modalities that we will be describing later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,will begin to make sense.\NIn the first place, how to hold that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of having a life-threatening illness,\Nsuch as cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How to hold that? What to think of that?\NWell, we have two ways we can go
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,about it. We can go up or we can go down.\NAny kind of a confront, such as a death in the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,any kind of a serious illness or setback in a person's life,\Nwe always have that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go down into feeling sorry for ourselves as victims,\Nwe can go down into self-pity, depression, despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,become suicidal,\Nor we can see it as a challenge, as an opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as a springboard to a greater awareness.\NOver and over these confronts come up in our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,until we seize the opportunity\Nand realize that this is the springboard to a greater awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so?\NBecause the ordinary events in life don't have the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't have the energy.\NIt takes max duress for a person to stop in their tracks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to question the realities of all the things\Nthat they have believed up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind will ordinarily not undertake\Nthe enormous energy expenditure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of reorienting itself\Nand getting a new different point of view about life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is real,\Nunless it has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So this necessary growth, then,\Nwill only happen when we're up against a major confront.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way, the first thing to get about the cancer\Nor the serious illness, whatever it may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the purpose of this major confront\Nis for us to grow and to grow rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the first message.\NMessage number one is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time to grow,\Nand to grow as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we have a certain time limit\Nwith most of these fatal terminal illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that the mind says are fatal and terminal\Nbecome fatal and terminal because of the power of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If the mind thinks that this is fatal and terminal,\Nthen it will be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see now the beginning of the expression\Nof the power of belief systems, belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, one of the main messages,\Nwe want to get across today,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is that no one needs to come or be victim\Nof any illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I count amongst my friends,\Npeople who have conquered every illness known to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only reason I'm sitting before you today\Nand able to make this talk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I, myself,\Ndid exactly the same thing in my own personal life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,where I would have hemorrhaged to death\Nfrom a variety of illnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,all of which have remitted.\NAll of which have remitted,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,including that I don't wear glasses anymore.\NOne time I wore bifocals and trifocals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even vision itself went back to perfect.\NSo that, that perfection which is held in mind then
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,reflects itself in the progressive perfection of the body\Nand the letting go of this E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to understand that the body itself\Nis expressing what is held in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is merely an expression of the mind.\NThe body is nothing but an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is held in consciousness.\NIt is a reflector of what we are holding consciously or unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A person looks back in their mind and they'll say,\Nwell, I don't remember thinking about such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't remember thinking about it,\Nfind out if it's in your unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all you have to do is look and see if it's in your life.\NSo to help us create a different context,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of looking at life,\Na way of looking at experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a map from which we can understand\Nall the principles of self-healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we have over here on the blackboard\Noutlined a chart of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which we've utilized in other talks.\NAnd if you've seen some of the other tapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,just realize that the person who is watching this again\Nis not the same person who saw it the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because every time we go over this,\Nit's sort of like break-brain learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We learn it through familiarity.\NThe left brain is linear and logical
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and it gets things piecemeal sequentially.\NThe right brain circles over a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and by sheer exposure and familiarity,\Nit just gets the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we'll be talking about today\Nare really things that in your unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in the periphery of your mind,\Nyou actually know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to try to pull them together,\Nsynchronize them in some kind of a useful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So on the board we have,\Nwithin this is called the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and everywhere I give talks,\Nthey often call it the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the human ego,\Nthe self with a small s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which people refer to\Nwhen they say I or me, myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the self with a small s,\Nis the human ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all that collection of concepts,\Nimpressions, opinions, feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,conscious and unconscious.\NThe totality of that that goes up to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,make up what the person means\Nwhen they say me, I, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And within the box you see\Nthere are various levels of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are levels of consciousness,\Nstarting at the very lowest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and going up to the very highest.\NAnd they have all been calibrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the research that we've done\Nwith my co-workers, with Lorraine Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What we did was we found out\Nthe directions of the energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You see these energy fields\Nfrom courage on down
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,all go to the left,\Nindicating that they have an anti-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Destructive, do not support life,\Nenergy to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And all those from courage on up,\Nyou see the energy fields begin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to swing to the right.\NAnd as we get closer and closer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to the truth they become more powerfully\Nto the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And so then we notice that love\Nis way at the top of the scale
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and guilt, on the other hand,\Nis way at the bottom of the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Also they've been numerically calibrated\Nby some techniques which are very
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated and difficult\Nand advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't go into the techniques\Nwhich is a science in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But they can be confirmed by anyone\Nwho is familiar with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The direction of the energy fields,\Nthe calibrated numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,their relative powers,\Ncan be reaffirmed by anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in their own living room\Nusing just basics of kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And to learn about that I would recommend\Na book by John Diamond called
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Life Energy.\NIt used to be called
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Behavioral Kinesiology.\NIt's a way of testing out energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the relative powers,\Nand whether that thing is constructive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or destructive.\NVery helpful, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to test out medical treatment.\NYou hold the medication in your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have somebody test your strength\Nand you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,will this medication be good for me or not?\NIf the medication is not good for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your arm will go weak.\NIf it's good for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your arm will go strong.\NSo any kind of a treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,even the doses,\Nyou can test out and find out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what's good for you.\NIt's necessary then to know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,something about energy fields\Nbecause this is intimately related
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to cancer and cancer research.\NIf we calibrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if we say that death is zero,\Nthen we will discover that enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a Buddha,\Nto become conscious of the absolute truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at about 600.\NThat energy field known as bliss,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,those energy fields known as\Nillumination or enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then if we go down near the bottom\Nof the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll see for instance that apathy,\Nwhich calibrates at 50,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,has about half the energy of fear,\Nwhich calibrates roughly at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Grief at 75 has about half the energy of anger,\Nwhich calibrates at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Being neutral,\Nthat is to be detached or unattached,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at 250 has only half the energy of love,\Nwhich is at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All these are extremely important.\NBecause body, mind and spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,are actually all just one.\NIt's all the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just being reflected in different planes.\NIt's an artificial abstraction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to cause body or mind or spirit.\NIt is actually all the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All three are an expression of consciousness.\NAnd therefore this energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,if it is a reversed or a negative energy field,\Nis that negativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is destructive,\Ndestructive in all aspects of ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,right down to the biochemical level.\NSo we see that the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which has a name to the right of the energy field,\Nis expressed as a certain emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we want to know what our energy field is,\Nall we have to do is look at what is the emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-pity, for instance,\Nautomatically tells you what's happened with self-pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you are now in a negative energy field,\Nwhich calibrates at 50,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is weak indeed,\Nas compared to love, which is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The importance then we see immediately\Nof letting go of negative feelings and negative thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The negative energy of the feeling or the thought\Ntransmits itself through the acupuncture energy system,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,through the 12 meridians,\Nrunning down the body meridian,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and translates itself right into the energy of the body organ,\Nright into the cells of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I hate someone,\Nthe cells of my body get the energy of hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And where is hate?\NHate is right about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a very reversed and quite powerful now,\Nnegative force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,150 is a lot of power,\Ntwice as much power as 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Its power, therefore,\Nits capacity for destruction is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So suppressed anger,\Nsuppressed anger then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,has the capacity to change the energy fields\Nwithin the body's cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the power to actually change the programming\Nwithin the body's cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we are going to be talking about today\Nis the enormous power that mind has
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,over every aspect of the body's functioning,\Nright down to the smallest molecule, an atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been discovered that every atom is conscious.\NEvery molecule within the body
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is conscious.\NEvery physiological and chemical transaction
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes on in the body\Nis the result of a blueprint of that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,within consciousness.\NAll of them can be changed then
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,by changing consciousness.\NI say that from personal experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,not only clinical experience\Nand personal experience with friends and associates,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but of course with my own physical health.\NI watched my own body chemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,literally change\Nas I began to change
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what I was holding about that\Nwithin my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,within my consciousness.\NAnd I came upon that basic principle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,essential to healing\Nfrom all illnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what they are,\Nbecause the same principles really apply
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:20:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to all illnesses,\Nthat we are only subject to what we hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are only subject to what we hold in mind.\NIt's the mind's belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that we give power to\Nthat then manifests in the physical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical body then\Nis an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which we've been holding in mind.\NNow we've either been holding it consciously
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or unconsciously.\NSee, people say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,well I don't remember holding such a thought.\NWell, there is what Jung calls
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective consciousness.\NThe thought form is there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,within the collective consciousness.\NAnd unconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we can buy into,\Nsupport,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,give energy to\Na negative belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,without ever remembering it,\Nwithout consciously being aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly with cancer,\Nwe are dealing with something
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been given\Nso much emotional energy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the popular mind.\NAll the fear associated with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all the negative connotations,\Nall the thought forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, fear itself,\Nthe whole fear unconsciously,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,this energy field here,\Nyou see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is a negative energy field.\NTherefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if I am holding a lot of unconscious fear,\Nwhat happens is the fear now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,opens the door\Nto bring into my mind unconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,those things that are fearful.\NThose things that are fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course,\Ncancer falls into that which is fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so therefore,\Nwithout ever having believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am susceptible to cancer,\NI may discover
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is occurring within the body,\Nthat I have unwittingly bought in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to this collective belief system,\Nthe collective thought form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just look at this field a little bit\Nbecause it will give us a better orientation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to what we'll be talking about later.\NWe see that at the very bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is an energy field called guilt.\NIt calibrates at 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It says death is zero.\NWell, guilt is 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the emotion that goes with guilt?\NIt's one of self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And a great deal of research into this\Nin psychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the psychosomatic viewpoints of cancers,\Nreveals that there is a good deal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of unconscious self-hatred,\Nself-condemnation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,lack of acceptance of one's humanness\Nat a deep level.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll talk about how to heal those things\Nbecause that's the way we bring about a healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're interested in these talks in healing.\NSee?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a difference between treating,\Ncuring, and healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible to treat an illness,\Nto treat symptoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring about an amelioration,\Na capacity, let's say, to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In the many years that I had migraine headaches,\NI had duodenal ulcers, diverticulitis,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,gout, hypoglycemia,\Na whole variety of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I had vibration disease of the fingertips,\Nthreatening gangrene of the fingers and pillows and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Circulatory problems.\NAll of these illnesses, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,came about as a result of belief systems\Nand they all were accompanied by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,some degree of unconscious guilt.\NWe find that unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,accompanies all illnesses\Nno matter what they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a physical illness,\Nyou can just presume and you will be 100% right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is unconscious guilt\Nand without the unconscious guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,actually the disease cannot be there.\NWhy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which is,\Nover on the right you'll see the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is destructive,\Nthat which is accompanied by self-hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,can only operate in a negative energy field.\NThat's the secret of healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be like certain bacteria\Nwill only grow in a culture media
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.65,0:23:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,under certain conditions,\Ncertain temperatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:24:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,certain amount of light and atmospheric conditions.\NIf you change the conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the bacteria cannot live in that feature dish anymore\Nand they will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, that which is destructive,\Nthat which meets the unconscious need
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for the process of destruction,\Ncan only go on in an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which itself is negative\Nand allows the negative energy of destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to take place.\NNow that starts to give us a clue
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which heals.\NThat which the energy field goes to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in nature,\Nin nature you see the rotation of an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.29,0:24:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is all decisive.\NFor instance, a drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.35,0:24:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the chemical effect of a molecule\Nis totally dependent on whether it spins to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.35,0:24:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,or it spins to the left.\NLet's take dextroamphetamine sulfate as an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.35,0:24:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dextro meaning to the right.\NDextroamphetamine sulfate is so-called speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.35,0:25:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody is familiar in our culture\Nwith what the effect of speed is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.35,0:25:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Weight loss and the feeling of high excitability,\Ngrinding your teeth and finally manic attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.35,0:25:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Revolve, meaning to the left,\Namphetamine sulfate has no such effect whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.93,0:25:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same molecule\Nbut the rotation is in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.93,0:25:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rotation of an energy field then,\Nthese are nurturing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.31,0:25:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and will support life and healing.\NThese on the left are destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.31,0:25:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore that which is destructive\Nmust take place in a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.31,0:25:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, all you need to do to heal yourself\Nis to move from the negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.31,0:25:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,into a positive energy field.\NSelf-healing is so simple, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.31,0:25:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really, that's what it amounts to.\NWhat it amounts to is changing the predominant energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.31,0:25:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,within your consciousness from negative to positive.\NThen the question arises of how do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.31,0:26:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you see the physics of it,\Nthe science of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.31,0:26:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the metaphysics of it,\Nthe truth of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.31,0:26:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotional truth of it,\Nfrom medical, psychiatric,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.31,0:26:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,holistic viewpoints,\Nyou see why we should let go of these emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.31,0:26:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in order to become a goody-goody person,\Nbut frankly because to hang on to them will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.31,0:26:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All these things are,\Nwe mentioned kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.43,0:26:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See, with kinesiology you test somebody's strength\Nand they hold any thought
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.43,0:26:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that has to do with any of these things.\NSomething you feel guilty about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.43,0:26:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something you feel hopeless about,\Nsomething you're sad and grieving about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.43,0:26:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something you're afraid of.\NSomething that you're into wanting and desiring,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.43,0:26:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something you're angry about,\Nsomething you're prideful about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.43,0:26:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Some truth that you're denying,\Nsome worry, some craving,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.43,0:26:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,some regret, some loss,\Nsome form of self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.69,0:26:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And any time you do that,\Nthe body instantly goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.85,0:27:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it goes weak,\Nit means you just blew your acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.85,0:27:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means you blew the meridian\Nto the various bodily organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.85,0:27:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you just changed the chemical pattern,\Nthe reproductive pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.85,0:27:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're tearing up the cells.\NSo it's obvious that all we have to do to heal anything
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.46,0:27:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is to move out of a negative energy field\Nand into a positive energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.46,0:27:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the power of the healing increases.\NThe higher, the more positive the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.46,0:27:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why the holistic approaches have worked\Nwhere medical science has not been able to affect the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.46,0:27:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I myself, as I said, am a living example.\NWithout knowing what I'm talking about today,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.46,0:27:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be here to give this lecture.\NI would have died, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.46,0:27:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,22 and a half years ago of another disease\Nwhich preceded all the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.46,0:27:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A fatal progressive disease\Nwhich reversed itself right at the point of death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.46,0:27:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So guilt is the most injurious, you see,\Nbecause it's accompanied by self-hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.10,0:28:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and the process that it brings in\Nis automatically destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.10,0:28:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know that from the study of geomancy.\NGeomancy is the study of energy fields in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.10,0:28:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we study the effect of energy fields\Nin nature, we will find that a negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.10,0:28:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in nature is anti-life.\NIt does not support life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.10,0:28:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So if a canyon, the energy field in that canyon,\Nif it goes into a negative direction
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.10,0:28:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for a variety of reasons,\Nif the crossing of the ley line,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.10,0:28:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the cutting, like I know the situation where a dam\Ncut the ley line, reversed the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.10,0:28:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,now the lives of everyone along that ley line\Nwere influenced in a negative direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.10,0:28:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, in a way, you see it's impersonal.\NThis energy field then has a destructive effect
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.10,0:28:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,within nature itself.\NAnd because you are part of nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.10,0:28:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have to suffer the loss\Nthat comes out of that destructive quality
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.54,0:28:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy field.\NSo, obviously then, letting go of guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.54,0:29:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and letting go of unconscious guilt\Nis crucial to recovering from any serious disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.54,0:29:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,especially cancer, where lack of self-esteem\Nand self-hatred and fear play such a predominant part
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.54,0:29:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next energy field above this\Nto be accompanied by hopelessness and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.64,0:29:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is called apathy, which is an energy field of 50\Nand the world view, the view of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.64,0:29:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes out of that is one of hopelessness.\NTo fall into self-pity and hopelessness then
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.64,0:29:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is to allow yourself to be overtaken\Nand become victim of an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.64,0:29:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which favors the progression of the cancer.\NSo what about that is grief?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.18,0:29:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, when people first get a cancer,\Nthey'll have a diagnosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.18,0:29:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,especially if they're a younger person.\NThey will say, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.18,0:29:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And go into regret, a feeling of loss and despondency.\NThe world now begins to look sad, life looks sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.18,0:30:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and they can then become the victim of this energy field.\NI keep repeating energy field because I want you to see
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.18,0:30:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,your own innocence in this matter.\NIt's because of your own innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.18,0:30:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that you literally allow yourself\Nto be run by this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.18,0:30:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The stage above that, the one\Nthat's also very prevalent
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.18,0:30:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in patients who develop cancer is fear.\NYou know, fear with a very negative energy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.18,0:30:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has more power now, an energy field of 100.\NThe world looks frightening, life looks frightening,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.18,0:30:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and God begins to look almost punitive.\NWhat kind of a God is it that could give you cancer, etc.?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.18,0:30:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the process of life itself begins to feel deflated.\NThe person is tempted to become dispirited,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.18,0:30:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,de-energized, and give in to the destructiveness,\Nto allow the thing to progress, unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.73,0:30:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can begin to desire something better for yourself\Nthan being the victim, being the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.73,0:30:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people I know recovered from all these illnesses\Ndid not settle for being victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.73,0:31:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They all began to desire something better for themselves.\NThere must be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.73,0:31:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And they began to research and began to look outside\Nof this traditional medical model.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.73,0:31:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?\NThey said, Doctor, well, is that all it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.73,0:31:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, is that all you got to offer?\NWell, it's going to take more than that to heal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.73,0:31:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And they began to find out,\Nis there something else that can heal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.73,0:31:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of that desire, out of the anger at being victim,\Nsee, we can use the energy fields of these emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.73,0:31:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in a constructive way.\NSo we can use the energy fields of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.14,0:31:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my own stepdaughter, you know, years ago,\Nfrom Hodgkin's disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember her going through\Na lot of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.14,0:31:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Being angry.\NAngry enough to begin to investigate and research
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.14,0:31:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and see what can be done about this.\NAngriness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.14,0:31:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the anger can be used constructively.\NThe anger, I don't have to be victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.14,0:32:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to give in to this thing.\NAnd to begin to take pride in our ability
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.14,0:32:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to expand our own consciousness.\NThe answer, as you look into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.14,0:32:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is there more that can be done?\NOf course, it is yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.14,0:32:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin to take pride.\NAnd now, to move up to a very decisive point
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.14,0:32:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,called courage.\NYou see, what happens at courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.27,0:32:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,not only does the energy field go all the way up to 200,\Nwhich is twice the energy of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.27,0:32:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,twice the energy of fear,\Nbut what is more important
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.27,0:32:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the direction of the energy field has changed.\NIt's gone from negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.27,0:32:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,from a field which supports that which is destructive,\Nand it has suddenly now gone neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.30,0:32:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, these energy fields down here are like an antenna.\NThey're like an antenna tuned to the negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.30,0:32:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So the energy field which surrounds the human body\Nis like an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.82,0:32:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it's tuned to the negative,\Nit draws to itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.82,0:32:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It draws to itself that which is destructive.\NAnd the body, of course, is right in the way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.82,0:33:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of that destructive energy field\Nand gets hit by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.82,0:33:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the negativity,\Nthe destructiveness expressing itself through the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.82,0:33:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,hitting the body, expressing itself.\NAnd in this particular case of cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.82,0:33:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it draws our attention to the fact\Nthat there is some error involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.82,0:33:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There is some error.\NThe courage to begin to look and see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.82,0:33:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is perhaps some error.\NThe way I've been holding life,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.82,0:33:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the way I've been holding my belief system,\Nthe way I think about myself
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.42,0:33:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps has been an error.\NSo one of the things about this level here of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.42,0:33:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is the beginning,\Nthe beginning, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.42,0:33:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of knowing.\NOur expression of that is humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.42,0:33:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage is expressed by humility.\NAnd now the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.42,0:33:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,our view of the world begins to change.\NOut of hopeless, out of sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.42,0:33:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,out of frightened, out of frustrating,\Nout of competitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.68,0:34:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,out of opportunistic and status.\NIt suddenly moves up to a world of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.61,0:34:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So the doors begin to open.\NBelow this, the mind is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.61,0:34:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It thinks it knows the answer.\NIt thinks it knows the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.61,0:34:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we have the courage,\Nwhat happens is the mind begins to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.61,0:34:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it says,\NI bet there's answers I don't even know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.61,0:34:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I don't even know the right questions to ask.\NAnd the minute we begin to open ourselves up,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.61,0:34:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is we become empowered.\NSee the process over on the right,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,when we have the courage to have an open mind,\Nis when we become empowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.61,0:34:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So below this, these are all states of powerlessness.\NAll states of victimhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.61,0:34:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we move up to an energy field of 200,\Nthe capacity to face the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.61,0:34:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to take responsibility for it.\NSee, the thing about victim
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.61,0:34:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is victim doesn't take responsibility.\NVictim says, well, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.06,0:35:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I got this is because of the bacteria.\NAnd the reason I got this is because of the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.06,0:35:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I got this is because of the cancer cells.\NIt's always something outside of oneself,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.06,0:35:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of one's consciousness.\NThat one is the victim of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.06,0:35:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No one begins to own that I've had something to do with it.\NWhat's happening in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.06,0:35:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is the result of something that I've been holding in mind.\NThe situation right above courage
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.30,0:35:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is a level called neutral.\NSo see, at neutral, the arrow has now gone to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.30,0:35:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the energy field has jumped up to 250.\NThe emotional state of that is called detached or non-attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.30,0:36:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The process going on in consciousness\Nis one of being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.37,0:36:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One experiences the okayness of life\Nand experiences a new and greater freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.37,0:36:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be expressed, let's say,\Nin serious illnesses or serious situations
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.37,0:36:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because all serious situations,\Nsee, call forth the same need
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.37,0:36:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to confront truth within yourself\Nand ascertain what is your position about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.69,0:36:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be expressed, let's say, as fatalism.\NFatalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.91,0:36:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that we had during the war,\Nlet's say, when I was in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.91,0:36:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that the bullet, you know,\Nthat's meant for you has your name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.91,0:36:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point of being afraid of bullets\Nbecause if it hasn't got your name on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.91,0:36:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not going to hit you anyway.\NThat can be expressed as karma, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.91,0:36:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever is going to be is destiny.\NKarma is the way it's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.91,0:36:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fatalistic position\Nis a certain peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.91,0:37:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain peace of mind.\NWe are detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.91,0:37:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person with cancer who reaches that says,\Nwell, look, if I survive, I survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.91,0:37:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I don't, I don't.\NYou know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.91,0:37:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing the best I can.\NIf I make it, I make it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.91,0:37:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I don't, I don't.\NI'm prepared to go in either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.91,0:37:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is certainly a far more comfortable position,\Nyou know, than to be in grief about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.91,0:37:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,self-pity, anger, resentment, arrogance, denial.\NPeople go into denial
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.91,0:37:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and deny they have the cancer, you know?\NThey will come up with a thought
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.91,0:37:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's been cured and all.\NWithout having gone through the necessary work
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.26,0:37:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring about, bring that about\Nas a reality in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.26,0:37:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's sort of magical thinking.\NWe can move above that to a willingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.71,0:37:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a friendly view of the world\Nwhere we see life is promising and hopeful,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.71,0:37:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and we discover, yes, there are answers.\NYes, there are answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.78,0:37:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of people walking around.\NWe have had terminal, fatal,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.78,0:38:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,given up all hope diseases of all kinds,\Nincluding cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.87,0:38:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened here is we've introduced intention,\Nincreased one's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.87,0:38:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,increased one's power,\Nup to accepting the fact that, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.87,0:38:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you can let go of this illness,\Nand there are healing modalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.87,0:38:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our harmonious world\Nin which there are lots of people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.87,0:38:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who have recovered from these illnesses\Nwho are only too happy to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.87,0:38:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the truths that they have discovered.\NWhy? Because they experience God
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.87,0:38:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,as that which is merciful.\NThe people at the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.87,0:38:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,experience God as punitive.\NAnd even if they don't believe in God,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.87,0:38:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,they believe in self-punishment\Nin one form or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.87,0:38:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,or pain and suffering.\NAnd feeling adequate, feeling confident,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.87,0:38:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, that there is an answer,\Nbegins a transformation of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.87,0:38:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves us up to the willingness to be coming\Ninto this energy field called love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.87,0:38:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a crucial level because\Nthe energy field of love is the one that heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.87,0:39:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All those organizations of people\Nwho are very famous for their capacity to heal,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.58,0:39:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcoholics Anonymous being probably\Nthe most famous on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.58,0:39:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,hopeless, progressive, chronic,\Nintractable disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.58,0:39:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for which there is no answer,\Nand medicine admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.61,0:39:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no cure for the condition.\NAnd yet, here is an incurable, progressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.61,0:39:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,disease that destroys every organ of the body,\Nincluding sanity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.61,0:39:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know there are half a million people\Nwalking around who have totally
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.61,0:39:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and 100% recovered from it.\NIn fact, their lives have been transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.64,0:39:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because there again, the affliction\Nwas used as a springboard
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.64,0:39:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to a greater consciousness\Nand a greater awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.64,0:39:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To move into a commitment\Nto that which is loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.64,0:39:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And we said the nature of it is unconditional love.\NNot the conditional love of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.64,0:40:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will love you if you will do this\Nor you will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.67,0:40:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To move into this begins a process\Ncalled revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.67,0:40:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins the release within the mind,\Nwithin the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.67,0:40:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of certain chemicals we call endorphins.\NSo, all these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.02,0:40:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have within the mind,\Nhave within the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.02,0:40:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,concomitant changes in the enzymes.\NThere are neurotransmitter changes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.02,0:40:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there is the release of whole,\Nopening of whole banks of neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.02,0:40:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, the person\Nhas moved into lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.18,0:40:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a healing energy field,\Nhas at their disposal
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.18,0:40:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the utilization of millions\Nand millions of neurons
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.18,0:40:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which people who are\Nin a negative emotional state
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.18,0:40:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,do not have at their fingertips.\NAnd therefore, they have assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.82,0:40:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So to move into the energy field\Nof unconditional love then
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.82,0:40:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,starts the healing process\Ngoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.50,0:41:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that when we calibrated\Nwe found that the healing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.69,0:41:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,healing occurs in an energy field\Nwhich you calibrate at about 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.69,0:41:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the energy field\Nof the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.26,0:41:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do we bring about\Nthe self-healing then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.26,0:41:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we have to let go\Nof a number of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.26,0:41:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to let go of unconscious guilt.\NWe have to discover,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.26,0:41:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I unearth that\Nwhich I feel guilty about?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.26,0:41:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin a self-questioning process.\NIn order to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.26,0:41:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the person is fearful.\NThey say, well, even if it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.26,0:41:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,would heal my cancer,\NI'm afraid I can't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.26,0:41:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because if I start opening Pandora's box\NI'm going to be swamped
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.26,0:41:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,by all the negativity and the guilt\Nthat I have suppressed and repressed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.26,0:41:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and pushed out of awareness\Nall my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.33,0:41:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we need some kind of tools,\Nsome kind of a practical way
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.33,0:42:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to process these things\Nand to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.35,0:42:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we need a context,\Na way in which to hold
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.35,0:42:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all that comes up\Nin this self-investigative process.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.35,0:42:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore we need a tool,\Nthe realization of what has been
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.35,0:42:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the basis of all our behavior\Nall of our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.64,0:42:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A context, a way to hold that\Nso that as it comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.64,0:42:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the guilt is automatically wiped out\Nby a higher understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.02,0:42:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to realize that\Nwe've committed exactly one sin,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.02,0:42:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the word in quotes.\NWe have been committing exactly one sin
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.02,0:42:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout our life,\Nand it's the same sin over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.02,0:42:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is that everything we ever did,\Nour intentions and our purposes,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.02,0:42:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was coming out\Nof the thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.02,0:42:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this will bring about happiness.\NIt's very important to know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.02,0:42:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize that the reason\Nwe did what we did at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.06,0:42:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we thought that\Nthat was necessary for our survival
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.06,0:43:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and our survival was necessary\Nfor our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.06,0:43:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so everything we did,\Nwe did in the name of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.06,0:43:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocent thought\Nthat this will bring us happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.18,0:43:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting happiness is the basic\Nof all human emotions, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.34,0:43:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the basic premise,\Nthe most primitive illusion of all
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.34,0:43:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it is the body\Nthat is the source of my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.34,0:43:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the fear of death\Nis really, if I lose the body
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.34,0:43:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lose the source of happiness,\NI will lose consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.50,0:43:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are spiritually aware,\Nof course this is nonsense,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.50,0:43:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because they no longer identify\Nwith the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.50,0:43:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I am awareness,\Nif I am consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.50,0:43:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which comes a knowingness\Nof what is happening within mind
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.50,0:43:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and within body,\Nthen body is the bottom rung
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.50,0:43:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,on the ladder, you see.\NConsciousness is totally unaffected
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,about what it is conscious of.\NSo we need to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.50,0:44:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of these negative emotions\Nand let go of suppressing them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.50,0:44:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and repressing them.\NAnd we have to have a tool to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.50,0:44:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is to let go of resisting them\Nas they come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.86,0:44:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to keep our eye on the fact\Nthat consciousness innately within itself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.86,0:44:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is innocent.\NThe nature of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.95,0:44:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is the innocence of the child.\NHow did we begin to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.78,0:44:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the things that we began to believe\Nas we grew older?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.78,0:44:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We look at the child and we see\Nhow innocent and trusting it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.78,0:44:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It is completely lacking in guile.\NWe know that its motivations
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.78,0:44:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,are pure, in at least our understanding\Nof purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.58,0:44:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that later become\Nthe consciousness of the adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.58,0:44:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the program\Nthat the child buys
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.58,0:44:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and buys into,\Nthe fact that it's programmable
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.74,0:44:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of the very nature\Nof innocence itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.74,0:44:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the child is innocent\Nand trusting that it begins
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.74,0:45:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to buy and believe everything\Nthat it hears,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.74,0:45:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,including all the thoughts\Nthat later express themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.74,0:45:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as cancer having to do\Nwith self-condemnation,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.90,0:45:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,fearful thoughts,\Nthoughts of rejecting oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.90,0:45:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and its expression of its humanness.\NAnd so to heal cancer then
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.90,0:45:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we need an approach,\Na willingness to heal ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.90,0:45:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by means of compassion.\NTo come from compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.90,0:45:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that is our greater,\Nour higher self,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.90,0:45:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding that out of innocence\Nall these belief systems came about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does the belief system\Nexpress itself in daily life?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.90,0:45:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It expressed itself as the thought\Nthat if I do this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.90,0:45:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or I have that,\Nthen I will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.90,0:45:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And so does,\Nhow does grief or loss
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.90,0:45:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,affect us?\NThe reason it affects us
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.97,0:45:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is we thought that was going to be\Na source of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.97,0:46:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're regretting is what we see\Nwhen we're angry
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.97,0:46:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because some obstacle\Nstands between
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.97,0:46:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the way of ourselves,\Nour intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.97,0:46:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what we want,\Nand that which we consider
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.19,0:46:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the source of happiness.\NSo if we go back to the board here,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.19,0:46:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we ask what is the illusion?\NWhat is the illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.19,0:46:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that was held in consciousness\Nnow expressing itself in the form of cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.19,0:46:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the illusion was\Nall these levels from courage on down,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.19,0:46:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,growth,\Nwe all thought that the source of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.19,0:46:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,was something outside of myself.\NThat something outside of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.38,0:46:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,has the power\Nto make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.38,0:46:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute I give away my power\Nand project it outside of myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.38,0:46:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I put myself in a negative energy field,\NI set myself up
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.38,0:46:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,as a victim.\NNow the unconscious purpose of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.12,0:47:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is to prove that you are a victim.\NAnd the test of cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.12,0:47:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is the test of whether or not\Nyou will continue
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.12,0:47:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to go along with this\Nand buy into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.50,0:47:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,95% of the world does.\NWhat I'm talking to today
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.50,0:47:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are the 5% of the people\Nwho are willing to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.50,0:47:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and become conscious.\N95% of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.50,0:47:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the ego would rather be right\Nand have you dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.60,0:47:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego would rather be right\Neven if it costs you your life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.60,0:47:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than give up the position\Nthat I am the innocent victim
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.60,0:47:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or something outside of myself.\NOnce you see your true innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.40,0:47:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then you don't need\Nthe pseudo-innocence of victimhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the owning of true innocence,\Nyou don't need
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.50,0:47:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the pseudo-innocence of victimhood.\NInasmuch as there is no victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.50,0:47:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,there was only a belief system\Nin the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.66,0:47:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which we kicked up out of our innocence.\NThe thought, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.23,0:48:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that success brings us happiness\Nis probably the most notorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.23,0:48:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As every middle-aged business man\Nwho has become successful knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.23,0:48:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what he gets out of his success\Nis a daily headache and exhaustion
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.23,0:48:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and a number of lawsuits\Nand some greed and envy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.23,0:48:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,from his colleagues.\NHe says to himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.23,0:48:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,where is all the happiness\Nthat success was supposed to bring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.23,0:48:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's brought me some pleasures,\Na nice car, a nice apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.23,0:48:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a nice address, and nice clothes.\NBut those things are not happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.23,0:48:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because worldly success\Nis an energy field of about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.23,0:48:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,120.\NSo worldly success
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.23,0:48:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,does not bring about the thing\Nand therefore the disillusionment
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.23,0:48:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the feeling of guilt.\NHow does the guilt come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.23,0:48:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The guilt comes about\Nas a result of feeling that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.23,0:48:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we have sold ourselves out subtly,\Nthat we have sold out
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.33,0:48:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth about ourselves.\NSo to recover from cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.33,0:49:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,or any other illness,\Nwe have to reconnect
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.33,0:49:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with our own intrinsic innocence,\Nwhich has been totally unaffected
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.33,0:49:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,by all of life's events,\Nto reown that level of awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.33,0:49:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of self,\Nwhich is beyond all worldly events.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.33,0:49:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something within us remains the same\Nno matter what is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.33,0:49:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in our life experience.\NSomething has been unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.33,0:49:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something that wakes up\Nthe first thing in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.33,0:49:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, before you realize where you are,\Nbefore you realize what day it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.33,0:49:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,before you realize what it is\Nyou're supposed to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.49,0:49:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When you wake up into that state of awareness\Nyou are much closer to the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.49,0:49:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own higher self\Nand you will realize it is totally unaffected,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.49,0:49:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it is beyond all of that.\NIt's only when your consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.49,0:49:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,comes down,\Ncomes down into the world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.49,0:49:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of concrete thought\Nyou say, oh yes, it's Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.87,0:49:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and oh yes, I have to go.\NNow you're coming down into the level
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.87,0:50:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of concrete thought.\NYou are really leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.94,0:50:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,being closed to the truth of that\Nwhich is beyond all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.94,0:50:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So we re-own then\Nthe capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.06,0:50:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to decide what our position will be\Nabout life's events.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.06,0:50:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things which bring about\Nextreme duress.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.54,0:50:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can become victims\Nor we can see it as a springboard
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.54,0:50:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcending that.\NThe first thing we have to let go of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.38,0:50:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is unconscious guilt.\NAnd that's why something like
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.38,0:50:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Course of Miracles\Nwhich has become very famous
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.38,0:50:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the state in which I live,\Nin which I live now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.38,0:50:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a day which is\NForgiveness Day
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.41,0:50:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's taken directly out of The Course of Miracles.\NThe Course of Miracles is a teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.14,0:50:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of love and forgiveness\Nand the letting go of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.14,0:50:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And many of the people I know\Nwho've recovered from cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.14,0:51:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and multiple sclerosis\Nand other serious debilitating illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.14,0:51:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,have done so as a result\Nof this particular
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.14,0:51:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,or other courses which are similar.\NThey are designed to show us
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.14,0:51:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,how to change our point of view\Nand how to let go of condemnation
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.14,0:51:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of ourselves and others.\NHow to let go of guilt and fear
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.14,0:51:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to move ourselves\Ninto the willingness to be loving
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.14,0:51:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and forgiving and compassionate.\NOut of that comes the desire to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.14,0:51:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So in our self-healing then\Nwe need to almost like
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.37,0:51:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,take ourselves in our own arms\Nbecome that which is compassionate
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.56,0:51:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and healing\Nbecause all of us have the healer
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.56,0:51:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all of us have within us the healer\Nand we begin now
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.56,0:51:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to heal our humanness.\NSee?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.72,0:51:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get rid of the ego?\NNot by making it an enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.72,0:51:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,not by trying to attack it\Nnot by getting into an adversary position
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.72,0:51:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with it\Nbut by loving it out of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.72,0:52:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We literally dissolve the ego\Nthrough compassion and love
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.72,0:52:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and understanding.\NWhen you see that anything
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.04,0:52:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you've ever done in your lifetime\Nwhen you can really see that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.04,0:52:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when your main intention\Nis to understand it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.42,0:52:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so that out of compassion it becomes healed\Nwhen we do this with other people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.42,0:52:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when we let go of the desire to be judgmental\Ntowards ourselves and towards other people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.42,0:52:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then what happens is\Nour own energy field begins to move
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.42,0:52:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in a positive direction.\NSee, cancer cannot grow
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.42,0:52:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in a positive energy field\Nit can only grow in a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.42,0:52:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we look over here\Nwe see that love
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.42,0:52:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one that's available\Nto all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.42,0:52:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The commitment to unconditional love\Nwhat is that kind of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.42,0:52:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about\NHollywood style emotionalism
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.42,0:52:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that sentimentality\Nthat attachment, that dependency
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.42,0:52:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that mutual control back and forth.\NInstead we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.42,0:53:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,an intention\Nthat's described as lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.42,0:53:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to commit oneself\Nto nurture and support
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.42,0:53:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all of life.\NNo matter what it's expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.42,0:53:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what it's expression.\NSee, when you think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.42,0:53:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,life flows equally\Ninto the saint
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.42,0:53:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and into the criminal.\NLife is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.42,0:53:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is the God within\Nmakes no judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.42,0:53:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It flows equally into all.\NAnd as it says in the scripture
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.42,0:53:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the rain falls equally on all.\NTo move out of judgmentalism
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.42,0:53:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because that is the lesson\Nin that example.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.42,0:53:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Life flows equally into all\Nso we allow our unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.74,0:53:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to support the truth of everyone\Nincluding ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.74,0:53:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our own capacity for self-healing.\NOur own, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.74,0:53:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That I and I alone\Nhave the power to make that decision
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.74,0:53:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,about whether I'm willing\Nto go through the necessary inner work
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.74,0:54:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring about a healing\Nof this illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.58,0:54:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To bring about a healing of the person\Nwho has that illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.58,0:54:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the difference between\Ncure and heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.58,0:54:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See, treating is treating a symptom.\NCuring is curing the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.64,0:54:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But healing is healing the person.\NAnd so we set our intention then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.64,0:54:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on accomplishing that\Nwhich is peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.64,0:54:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The accomplishment of peace of mind.\NBecause that is the end result
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.64,0:54:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of healing.\NThe end result of healing
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.64,0:54:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is an inner tranquility.\NNot an indifference
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.64,0:54:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to what happens to the body\Nbut a transcendence of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.64,0:54:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the longer do we identify\Nas that physical thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.64,0:54:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It belongs to us.\NIt's part of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.64,0:54:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is within us\Nbecause we realize that we are more
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.64,0:54:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,than the physical body.\NSo the healing of cancer depends
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.64,0:55:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on realizing that we are\Nthe one who decides
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.64,0:55:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are greater than\Nthe physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.64,0:55:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That it is within the power of consciousness\Nto call forth the healer
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.64,0:55:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,within us.\NAnd realize some of the consciousness techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.64,0:55:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that we talked about today.\NSee, what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.74,0:55:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when you start to ask yourself\Ncan I heal myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.74,0:55:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this healable?\NWhat within me needs to be healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.74,0:55:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the cancer is only the outer\Nphysical expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.74,0:55:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It still doesn't tell us, literally\Nin our own particular case
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.74,0:55:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,what needs to be healed.\NWhen I had severe diverticulitis
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.57,0:55:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,recurrent for many years\Nand I would land in the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.89,0:55:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the last time I had it\NI almost expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.81,0:55:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To really get rid of it\Nfollowing these general principles
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.81,0:55:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, it improved\Nand it got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.38,0:56:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't have it for some years.\NAnd then suddenly something occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.48,0:56:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life\Nand I had a recurrence
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.48,0:56:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had the worst attack of diverticulitis\NI've ever had in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.48,0:56:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain was overwhelming\Nand the cramping and the bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.48,0:56:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the whole thing started all over again.\NAnd I asked what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.64,0:56:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?\NI began to question within.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.64,0:56:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I began to question within\Nthen came to me a technique
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.64,0:56:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of going way, way back\Nand discovering the exact
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.64,0:56:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the precise meaning\Nwhich lay within this particular illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.64,0:56:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And so for most of us\Na general
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.12,0:56:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,following the general laws of healing\Nis sufficient to bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.12,0:56:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a recovery from an illness.\NFor some of us there is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.12,0:56:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a very particular lesson\Nthat a given illness has.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.12,0:56:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A very particular message.\NAnd the illness will get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.76,0:56:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But then something will linger on\Nor a recurrence may occur
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.76,0:57:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the purpose of that\Nis to bring about your learning
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.76,0:57:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a specific hidden message\Nthat you missed
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.76,0:57:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and please get it this time.\NThe message of all of this for us then
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.98,0:57:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is that these major\Nconfronts of life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.98,0:57:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,are something\Nthat transforms us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.98,0:57:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the power to transform.\NSo if you give the cancer within you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.98,0:57:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,your blessing\Nand you say thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.98,0:57:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are giving me the power\Nto transform my consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.21,0:57:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to expand my awareness\Nthen you will be in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.66,0:57:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,very thankful.\NMany people who have recovered
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.66,0:57:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,from these illnesses\Nwill look back and they all say
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.66,0:57:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how grateful I am\Nthat that arose in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.66,0:57:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How grateful I am\Nthat this cancer came into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.66,0:57:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and has brought me to the level\Nof awareness that I am today.
